The reason the form-related elements aren't included is that there were no use cases that needed them. You should elaborate on your use case on the mailing list if you want this changed in the spec.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4">zcorpan</a> — Mon Aug 30, 2010 9:42 am</p><hr />
